name: SGIN 10 Inch KidsTablet, 4GB RAM 64GB ROM, Android 12 Tablet for Kids with Case, Octa-Core 2.0Ghz Processor, 1280 * 800 IPS, 2MP+5MP Camera, 6000mAh, GPS, WiFi, Bluetooth (Purple)
feature_bullets: 【4GB+64GB Large-Capacity Tablets】This baby tablet is equipped with 4GB high-speed LPDDR4 random-access memory, enable to quicker launch speed, smoother interacting with the WiFi tablet for kids. 64GB large-capacity storage space, supporting 256GB TF card expansion. you can store as many ebooks, songs, pictures, videos, and games as you like and complete a variety of tasks by this toddler tablet.,【High-Performance Kids Tablet】 This Android 12 tablet is equipped with MT8183, with a high-performance 8-core CPU that has a frequency operation of up to 2GHz and can run multiple programs smoothly and handle multi-threaded tasks perfectly. Pre-install Android 12 OS with Google Mobile Service support, which can be easily operated by both kids and all age groups. In addition, 500 gram lightweight design making it comfortable to hold and easy to carry on the go.,【Full HD IPS Screen 10 inch Tablet & Proof-case】This 10 in tablet is equipped with a 10.1 inch high definition 1280*800 IPS screen with a narrow bezel design and built-in dual-speaker to provide you with more stunning auditory and visual effects. This kids tablets designed with case that can protect your tablet for kids 3-7 against dust,bumps, and drops off. The hollow protective case has the function of heat dissipation.,【Multifunctional hardware & ports Support】Naclud kids tablet with case build-in a clear 2MP front cam and a 5MP rear camera, Bluetooth 5.0, dual-band Wi-Fi(2.4G/5G), dual speakers, a Type-C interface (fast charger included), a Micro TF slot, and 3.5mm headphone jack. Bring you a full range of audio-visual experience and meet the need in different usage scenarios.,【Long Battery Life】 Providing a 6000mWh rechargeable battery, the power-efficient google tablet is designed to last for up to 5-7 hours on one charge (according to different scenarios) and easily charge via the Type-C port and rest assured the battery will last, so that furthest meet kid’s usage needs on the move for playing and learning. It's a great gift for kids in Birthday, Christmas, and New Year.

name: 2024 Newest Android 13 Tablet with Keyboard 10 Inch 2 in 1 Tablets, 12GB RAM 128GB ROM 1TB Expand, Quad-Core 2.0GHz CPU Tablet PC, 5G WiFi 6 BT 5.0, 8MP Camera, Google Certified Tableta
feature_bullets: 【Newest Android 13 Tablet + Google Certification】Bnegynng Tablet is equipped with the latest Android 13 system, which has been upgraded in all aspects of system operation, with faster response time and more focus on user privacy and security. It also adds a lot of interesting and convenient operations, which greatly improves the user's operating experience. It is also Google GMS certified, so you can download the APP you want, such as Netflix, TikTok, YouTube, Yahoo, Twitter and other APP,【12GB RAM + 128GB ROM + 1TB Expandable】The Android 13 Tablet PC features memory expansion technology with 12GB RAM (6GB fixed memory, 6GB virtual memory) to make multitasking smooth; 128GB ROM to make the storage space super large. It also supports 1TB microSD card expansion (card not included) to download games, music or videos as you wish.,【Notebook and 2 in 1 Tablet with Keyboard】The 10 inch Android 13 tablet package includes a 10.1 inch tablets, a wireless keyboard and mouse, a protective case, and a flexible stylus, screen protector, This portable Android tablet also comes with an OTG connector and charger. 2 in 1 Tablet PC can fulfill all your needs at work and in everyday life.,【10.1 Inch HD IPS Screen and HD Camera】This Android 13 tablets features a 10.1 inch P+G FHD IPS high-definition screen with 1280x800 resolution for sharp, vibrant and lifelike images.Whether you're streaming your favorite movie or playing a video game, you'll be completely immersed in the visuals.The 10 inch tablet comes with an 8MP rear camera to clearly capture life's The 2MP front-facing camera provides excellent clarity during video calls.,【2.4G/5G Wifi 6 + BT 5.0 + 6000mAh】10 inch Wifi Tablet supports 2.0GHz high speed dual-band, can connect to any 2.4G + 5G WiFi 6 network, Bluetooth 5.0 function, wireless signal is more stable, transmission speed is faster, make the wireless device more power saving. Equipped with 6000mAh battery, the battery life is up to 10 hours, watching videos, playing games, reading e-books, listening to music and so on without worrying about the time, perfect for long-distance travel.

The tablet android is also equipped with a 5000mAh large-capacity battery for up to 8 hours of use and entertainment.,【Exclusive Kid-Proof Case】The tablet for kids equipped with high quality EVA material protective case that can avoid the damage caused by drops and bumps at play and against dust. At the same time, the 10 inch kids tablet also has its own stand, which is more convenient for children to study and play games.,【Perfect Gift for Kids】The newest toddler tablet is designed specially for kids ages 3 and up. It would be a great companion for kids to study and play. It's also the best gift selection for Children’s day, birthday, graduation ceremony, Easter, Christmas and Thanksgiving.
